Name: Head Shot
About the game: Take a role in a caroonish styled FPS multiplayer game. Choose among 5 characters and bunch of weapons and play Head Shot online with friends and strangers. Features: -5 classes (Assault, Sniper, Engineer, Medic, Machine Gunner); -Various types of weapons including Assaults, Equipments, Machine Guns, Pistols, Rocket Launchers, Shotguns and Snipers; -Vehicles; -Different game modes (currently Death Match and Team Death Match) Planned features: -More weapons; -More game modes; -More items and various other content that will bring more fun into the game. -Open chest system and various other stuff... More features coming soon.
